{"title_page": "Tales (film)", "text_new": "{{short description|2014 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Tales\n| image          = Ghesse-ha movie poster.jpg\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Rakhshan Bani-E'temad]]\n| producer       = \n| writer         = Rakhshan Bani-E'temad<br>[[Farid Mostafavi]]\n| starring       = [[Habib Rezaei]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = Koohyar Kalari\n| editing        = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{Film date|2014|8|28|[[71st Venice International Film Festival|Venice]]|df=yes}}\n| runtime        = 88 minutes\n| country        = Iran\n| language       = Persian\n| budget         = \n}}\n\n'''''Tales''''' ({{lang-fa|\u0642\u0635\u0647\u200c\u0647\u0627}} ''Ghesse-ha'') is a 2014 Iranian [[drama film]] directed by [[Rakhshan Bani-E'temad]]. It contains seven tales about different people.<ref>[http://www.salamcinama.ir/news/170/\u0645\u0639\u0631\u0641\u06cc-\u0641\u06cc\u0644\u0645-\u0647\u0627\u06cc-\u0633\u06cc-\u0648-\u062f\u0648\u0645\u06cc\u0646-\u062f\u0648\u0631\u0647-\u062c\u0634\u0646\u0648\u0627\u0631\u0647-\u0641\u06cc\u0644\u0645-\u0641\u062c\u0631-\u0642\u0635\u0647-\u0647\u0627-\u0639\u06a9\u0633-\u0647\u0627\u06cc-\u0641\u06cc\u0644\u0645-\u0648-\u067e\u0634\u062a-\u0635\u062d\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u0639\u0631\u0641\u06cc \u0641\u06cc\u0644\u0645\u200c\u0647\u0627\u06cc \u0633\u06cc \u0648 \u062f\u0648\u0645\u06cc\u0646 \u062f\u0648\u0631\u0647 \u062c\u0634\u0646\u0648\u0627\u0631\u0647 \u0641\u06cc\u0644\u0645 \u0641\u062c\u0631] ''Movie Mag''</ref> It was selected to compete for the [[Golden Lion]] at the [[71st Venice International Film Festival]],<ref name=\"Venice\">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |title=International competition of feature films |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Venice |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083927/http://www.labiennale.